    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, it's right that onStateChange doesn't allow for that use case per se, but start indeed follows that pattern perfectly.\n\nIf you want to instantiate InstantSearch but aren't yet ready to search, call `start` later. That's not a workaround but the intended way of using InstantSearch",
